    <item>
      <title>亚马逊取消美国杂货店的无收银系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/amazon-pulls-plug-on-cashierless-system-in-us-grocery-stores</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司(Amazon.com Inc.)正在从杂货店中移除其无收银员Just Walk Out系统，这是一项旨在让购物者免排队的雄心勃勃的技术的撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/amazon-pulls-plug-on-cashierless-system-in-us-grocery-stores</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:46:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BCE 触及 10 年低点，BMO 电信前景恶化后罗杰斯股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/canada-telecom-shares-drop-on-bmo-notes-on-rogers-bce-quebecor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在蒙特利尔银行资本市场 (BMO Capital Markets) 公布加拿大电信行业前景黯淡后，BCE Inc. 股价跌至十多年来的最低点，罗杰斯通信公司 (Rogers Communications Inc.) 遭遇 2024 年最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/canada-telecom-shares-drop-on-bmo-notes-on-rogers-bce-quebecor</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:09:55 GMT</pubDate>
